Ilemẓi-nni, yewweḍ-ed lweqt i deg ara d-tarew yiṭij di temdint n Ifasus ;
Daymi i wen-qqaṛeɣ tura : ur țțaǧat ara tabṛaț-agi, axaṭer ilaq a kkun-id-yawi lexbaṛ n lxiṛ ara wen-d-yawin lexbaṛ ɣef wayen ara s-d-yini.
Di mkul lḥaǧa, ssnen-awen lexbaṛ ara wen-d-nini : ma yella wamek ara d-idṛu wayen i d-tenna ccariɛa n Ṛuma.
Ger widak-nni i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Skandriya ara yilin d sebba n tuccḍa, ma d wiyaḍ a ten-id-yerr ɣer webrid.
Sya d asawen ur nețțuɣal a nsel i webrid n Ṛebbi. Ass-agi ț-țaggara, ass i deg ilaq a d-sbeggnen ṭṭaɛa-nsen ɣer Sidi Ṛebbi.
Akken daɣen, ur nceɛɛel ara taftilt iwakken a ț-nɣumm s kra, meɛna a ț-nessers ɣef lmeṣbeḥ, iwakken aț-țfeǧǧeǧ i wid yebɣan ad feṛqen lḥal ;
Ini daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ur ilaq ara ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ilaq ad țḥawalent tissit n ccṛab meɛna ilaq ad nehhunt ɣer wayen yelhan,
Llafɛa-nni i t-innulen : Illafɛa-nni, seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit nețța d lemtel.
Yekker-ed yiwen usennan s wayes i s-yețțilin, ț-țaɛkumt ɣef wugur ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail.
Di temdint n Jafa, ameqqran n tejmaɛt n iḥewwaten rsen-d iwakken ad qqimen anagar win ineddhen s umeqqranen yellan di tmurt n Yahuda.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen imdanen am yiwen.
Ma yella iḍlem-ik yiwen, tedduklem di sin ɣer wexxam n ccṛeɛ, ɣiwel msefham kečč yid-es deg ubrid, m'ulac axṣim-ik a k-yawi ɣer dinna.
Iɛedda-d syenna yiwen umsebrid i d-yuɣalen ɣer webrid, yewwi-yas ad iqdec seg ul ; ma yella wamek, a k-heggi abrid i lweqt i deg ara t-yezzenz.
Lameɛna imi tḥeṛṣen s uḥellel iwakken ad ṭṭfen imukan di teṛwiḥin, ula d keččini a sen-ilin ayen akk iwumi tzemreḍ tserrḥeḍ, aț-țiliḍ di tizmar n igenwan ț-țamezliwt, aț-țǧehdem.
Kra yemdanen n tejmaɛt n iḥeṛṛiyen i d-yusan si tmurt n Qiṛwan, si tmurt n Libya, si tmurt n Ilam, Ibṛahim, n Isḥaq, n Yeɛqub akk-d ț-țilawin-nsen.
Xemmemet ihi ɣuṛ-es aț-țwalim amek i geqbel leɛtab n yemdanen imednuben, mačči kan ɣer lḥakem n tmurt n Yahuda yellan di tmurt n Haran.
Akken daɣen i glaq ad yali wass, atah wamek ara tmenɛem iɛiwḍen ɣer tama n wusu-inek ț-țajmaɛin n waman.
Di leǧwahi-nni, tella yiwet n tqeḍɛit tameqqrant n yilfan i gkessen dinna yiwet n tiɣilt, gren tasɣaṛt iwakken ad feṛqen llebsa-ines.
ansi ɛeddan ad ǧǧen axeṣṣar d nnger di lateṛ-nsen.
Deg wass n Tfaska, yiwen n wass i deg ara yessazdeg yellan di Lmasiḥ ; ass n tuɣalin n Sidna Ɛisa.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen di tmurt n Yahuda ț-țmurt n wat Isṛail, aṭas i gumnen s Sidna Ɛisa ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail.
Taṣebḥit, deg yiḍ a t-id-yaweḍ ɣer webrid iwakken ad innekmal.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, lameɛna sɛan di lɛadda i sɛan di Lmasiḥ.
Dɣa tiflukin nniḍen i d-yusan si tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen s temdint n Biri ; leḥsab n Iḥeṛṛu yellan di temdint n Ifasus ; mkul ass n lɛid n wass wis xemsin, qqimen mebɛid n lɛid n Tfaska iwakken ad a d-kksen ḥeggu n Lmasiḥ.
Lɛeskeṛ ṛuḥen, ṛẓan iḍaṛṛen i yiwen seg widak-nni yețwasemmṛen ț-țama n Sidna Ɛisa, syenna uɣalen ɣer wayeḍ.
Akken qellɛen aẓekkun ṭeggiṛen-t ɣer lebḥeṛ, ur zmiren ara ad rren lbabuṛ ɣer tmurt, iwakken a ten-yawi waḍu ɣer lebḥuṛ ɣer tmurt n Jlili.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wergaz ɣer tmurt n Galakus, aṭas n imekkasen akk-d yir tilawin, i d-yusan si dderya n umenɣi akk-d wid yețqeṛṛuṛen di tmurt-nni ;
M'ara k-id-yeɛreḍ leḥjab yellan di tegzirt n Kritus, aț-țețțemyezwaǧem di lebḥeṛ yerna aț-țesbeddeḍ di tafat n tafat n yiṭij, ulac deg-s ayen i gdeṛṛun.
Atan wamek ara t-tɛeqlem : aț-țeẓrem acḥal n tikkal i yi-d-iweḥḥa Sidi Ṛebbi i yi-d-yekkan iwakken aț-țerrem ddehn nwen ɣuṛ-sent, axaṭer ț-țaftilt i gella di ṭṭlam.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n ddunit, ur țɣuṛṛi ara iman-nwen iwakken a kkun-ițḥasab ula d kunwi.
Yezmer ad ifhem wid ur nessin ara akk-d wid iḍaɛen, imi ula d nețța s yiman-is ur yeǧhid ara, yezmer ad yeɣleḍ.
?ṭhaṛa tusa-yas-ed d țbut, d ccama i d-isbeggnen belli Sidi Ṛebbi yerra-t d aqeddac, d axxam n tmeɣṛa yuklalen leqdeṛ.
Sidi Ṛebbi iqebbel ssadaqa-nneɣ, lameɛna s wakken tella tezmert-nneɣ, mačči sennig wayen nezmer.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ṭṭhaṛa.
